      "title": "<span id=\"#29836\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">federation</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(n.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>\"1721年，指“协议联盟”，源自法语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">fédération</i>，源自晚期拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">foederationem</i>（主格 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">foederatio</i>），是 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">foederare</i> 的动名词，该词源自拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">foedus</i> “契约，联盟”（源自 PIE 词根 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of *bheidh- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/*bheidh-\">*bheidh-</a> “信任，信赖，说服”）。</p>"
